It's the 31st of December, and the calendar is about to shed the last of its pages.
The world is ready to turn a new leaf, awaiting a new beginning, a new year!
But Maya and Meera head towards a park bench to meet and greet at exactly 6 PM. 
to visit the memories of their shared past together, like they have been doing 
religiously for over a decade.

